Format: 

+ (Sensor wire name / pin #) - (mbed pin)

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Humidity / Temp Sensor Wiring:

+ Pin 1 - Vout (3.3v)
+ Pin 2 - Data (p21)
+ Pin 3 - NC (not connected)
+ Pin 4 - GND

+ 4.7 kOhm resistor b/t VCC and Data
+ https://developer.mbed.org/cookbook/Grove-temperature--humidity-sensors

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Light Sensor Wiring:

+ Lead 1 - GND
+ Lead 2 - Data (p15)

+ Note: Orientation of leads doesn't matter
+ 10 kOhm resistor in PARALLEL b/t Lead 2 and Vout (3.3v)
+ https://developer.mbed.org/users/4180_1/notebook/using-a-photocell-to-determine-light-levels/

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Sharp IR Sensor (Using 3-pin connector cable):

+ Yellow Wire - Data (p16)
+ Black Wire - GND
+ Red Wire - Vout (3.3v)

+ 10 microfarad capacitor b/t black and red wires
+ https://developer.mbed.org/users/pharp6/notebook/sharp-ir-sensor-displayed-through-virtual-com-port/
